#How to Install

For installing or running secron,
please make the install.sh file executable
You can do that by opening terminal in this directory and issuing this command
Right click and select open in terminal
enter
  chmod +x install.sh

Now install.sh file is ready to execute

Now enter
  sudo sh install.sh
      or
  sudo ./install.sh
  
 to start the the installation.
 
Once the installation is complete, please read the doc/how-to.txt for usage options.
